Files in this component and their provenance:

  src/uat_decode.c, src/uat_decode.h
      Vendored from dump978 uat_decode.{c,h}. The ADS-B MDB decode path
      (uat_decode_hdr/sv/ms/auxsv, uat_decode_adsb_mdb, the base40
